    "headline": "Decisive Dividend Corporation Announces May 2026 Dividend",
    "summary": "Decisive Dividend Corporation (TSXV: DE) (the \"Corporation\") announced today that, in accordance with its current monthly dividend policy, the directors of the Corporation have declared a dividend of $0.045 per common share for the month of May 2026. The dividend is payable on May 15, 2026, to the shareholders of record at the close of business April 30, 2026.",
